### WhatsApp AI Agent — REST Client requests
### Requires VS Code extension: humao.rest-client

@agentUrl   = http://localhost:8000
@instance   = praveenIndia
@testPhone  = 918700082665

# =============================================================================
# HEALTH & METRICS
# =============================================================================

### Health check
GET {{agentUrl}}/health

###

### Metrics
GET {{agentUrl}}/metrics

# =============================================================================
# WEBHOOK — simulate incoming WhatsApp messages
# =============================================================================

### Simulate "Hi" message
POST {{agentUrl}}/webhook/evolution
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "messages.upsert",
  "instance": "{{instance}}",
  "data": [
    {
      "key": {
        "remoteJid": "{{testPhone}}@s.whatsapp.net",
        "fromMe": false,
        "id": "TEST001"
      },
      "message": {
        "conversation": "Hi! What products do you have?"
      },
      "messageType": "conversation",
      "messageTimestamp": 1700000000,
      "pushName": "Test User"
    }
  ]
}

###

